OL,4,G1410FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GAt The Grange Boutique Hotel in
OL,6,     GCumbria, Jackie and Nigel hope to
OL,7,     Gimpress with high-end suites. But
OL,8,     GSimon finds his room stifling and
OL,9,     Gthe breakfast eggs aren't all
OL,10,     Gthey're cracked up to be.
OL,11,G1440FFour in a Bed
OL,12,     GThe second visit is to Ruth and
OL,13,     GLucy's Rutland Luxury Lodges in
OL,14,     GGreetham. Most of their guests
OL,15,     Gfind luxury in abundance, but
OL,16,     GJackie and Nigel get hot and
OL,17,     Gbothered about the bedding.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
