OL,4,G1510FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GThe third visit is to The
OL,6,     GLeicester Arms in Kent, hosted by
OL,7,     Ghusbands Laurence and Danny. Some
OL,8,     Gguests get a spotless welcome,
OL,9,     Gbut Jackie and Nigel make dirty
OL,10,     Gdiscoveries.
OL,11,G1540FFour in a Bed
OL,12,     GThe final visit is to Oakover
OL,13,     GGuest House in Weston-super-Mare,
OL,14,     Ghosted by Simon Robinson and Ann
OL,15,     GWilson. The B&Bers are delighted
OL,16,     Gby the decor, but Lucy and Ruth
OL,17,     Gget a frosty reception...
