OL,4,G1615FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GIt's feedback time as the B&Bers
OL,6,     Gmeet to complain about breakfast
OL,7,     Geggs, dirty rooms and sleepless
OL,8,     Gnights. One owner's strategy
OL,9,     Gcomes under scrutiny, before the
